### Admin / permission / audit manual flow
### Usage:
### 1. LLM_PROVIDER=mock make env-smoke-up
### 2. make env-smoke-wait
### 3. make seed-dev
### 4. Run these requests top-to-bottom with VS Code REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP Client.
###
### Trace tip:
### Copy any response X-Trace-ID into Grafana/Tempo when observability is enabled:
### docker compose --env-file .env.smoke --env-file deploy/monitoring/observability.env.template --profile observability -f docker-compose.db.yml up -d

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@seedPassword = SeedPass123!
@adminUsername = seed_admin
@memberUsername = seed_member
@viewerUsername = seed_viewer
@inactiveUsername = seed_inactive


### Health - live
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health_check/live
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-health-live-001


### Health - DB ready
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health_check/db_ready
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-health-ready-001


### Auth - admin login
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Request-ID: manual-admin-login-001

username={{adminUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}


### Users - admin current user
# @name adminMe
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-admin-me-001


### Users - admin can query a seeded member
# @name memberLookup
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?username={{memberUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-admin-query-member-001


### Users - admin patches the seeded member, safe to run repeatedly
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{memberLookup.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-admin-update-member-001

{
  "max_tokens": 80000
}


### Auth - member login
# @name memberLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Request-ID: manual-member-login-001

username={{memberUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}


### Users - member current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-member-me-001


### Users - member tries admin-only user query, should return 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?username={{adminUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-member-forbidden-user-query-001


### Auth - inactive login, should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Request-ID: manual-inactive-login-001

username={{inactiveUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}


### Chat - member sends a non-stream query
# @name chatQuery
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-chat-query-001

{
  "query": "请回复一句话，说明后台权限测试链路正常。",
  "client_request_id": "manual-chat-client-001"
}


### Chat - idempotency repeat, should return the same logical answer for the same client_request_id
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-chat-query-repeat-001

{
  "query": "请回复一句话，说明后台权限测试链路正常。",
  "client_request_id": "manual-chat-client-001"
}


### Chat - member sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/sessions?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-chat-sessions-001


### Chat - member session detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/sessions/{{chatQuery.response.body.$.session_id}}?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-chat-session-detail-001


### Audit - latest events, admin only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-audit-list-001


### Audit - find admin user update audit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?request_id=manual-admin-update-member-001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-audit-find-update-user-001


### Audit - find chat audit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?request_id=manual-chat-query-001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-audit-find-chat-001


### Audit - member should not read audit events, should return 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?skip=0&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-member-forbidden-audit-001
